<html>
  <head>
    <title>Your order has been canceled</title>
    <style>
      html {
        background: #FFF9ED url(https://cherrystickers.herokuapp.com/assets/img/mail/background.png);
        font-family: sans-serif;
        color: #1E1E1E;
      }

      body {
        background: url(https://cherrystickers.herokuapp.com/assets/img/mail/stamp.png)no-repeat 90% 0%;
        background-size: 25%;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      h1 {
        margin-top: 5rem;
        font-size: 4rem;
        font-weight: lighter;
        color: #816350;
      }

      a {
        color: #816350;
        font-weight: bold;
      }

      .thank {
        width: 50vw;
        text-align: center;
        line-height: 180%;
        color: #816350;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
      }

      .info-holder {
        box-sizing: border-box;
        width: 50vw;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        padding: 2rem 5rem;
      }

      .title-numbers, .info-numbers {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
      }

      .item-title {
        margin-top: 2rem;
        font-size: 1rem;
        color: #1E1E1E;
      }

      .header-column, .item {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
      }

      .prior, .item p.prior {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        flex: 1;
        text-align: left;
      }

      h3, .item p {
        text-align: center;
        width: 5rem;
      }

      .large {
        margin-top: 4rem;
      }

      footer {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        margin-top: 2rem;
      }

      h4 {
        color: #816350;
        font-weight: lighter;
        font-size: 1rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }

      .item p, .info-numbers p {
        color: #816350;
      }

      p > img {
        height: 5rem;
        width: 5rem;
        margin-right: 1rem;
      }

      .total {
        width: 100%;
        text-align: right;
        border-top: 1px solid black;
        font-weight: lighter;
        font-style: italic;
        padding-top: 1rem;
      }

      .total > span {
        font-size: .8rem;
      }

      @media only screen and (max-width: 750px) {
        .info-holder {
          width: 90vw;
        }

        .thank {
          width: 90vw;
        }

        h1 {
          text-align: center;
        }

        body {
          background-position: top right;
        }
      }

      @media only screen and (max-width: 480px){
        .info-holder {
          width: 120vw;
        }

        body {
          background-size: 40%;
        }
      }

    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Your order has been canceled</h1>
    <p class="thank">Your Cherry order <b>{{data.orderId}}</b> has been <b>Canceled</b> on <b>{{orderDate}}</b>. Your payment will be tranfered on your paypal account soon. <br> We hope te see at our store.</p>
    <p class="thank">Questions? Suggestions? <a href="mailto:info@cherrystickers.be">Shoot us an email.</a></p>

    <footer>
      <h4>We hope to see you soon at our store!</h4>
      <h4>The Cherry Team</h4>
    </footer>

  </body>
</html>
